    <item>
      <title>Edit weight settings</title>
      <link>https://build.prestashop.com/test-scenarios/core/functional-1-7-8-x/test-cases/bo/shop-parameters/search/search/edit-weight-settings/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://build.prestashop.com/test-scenarios/core/functional-1-7-8-x/test-cases/bo/shop-parameters/search/search/edit-weight-settings/</guid>
      <description>Steps Set a weight settings to 0 (for example, product name)
Re-build entire index
Try to search in FO a product which has a unique name in this category (for example, a product with &amp;ldquo;unique&amp;rdquo; as a product name, and where &amp;ldquo;unique&amp;rdquo; is nowhere else)
Search should not have this product is the result
Set the weight settings back to it&amp;rsquo;s normal value, re-build index
Search the product in FO, it should be there</description>
